Definition: the dispersion of the Jews outside Israel
Example: from the destruction of the temple in Jerusalem in 587-86 BC when they were exiled to Babylonia up to the present time
Synonyms: dispersion, the, of, Jews, outside, Israel, from, destruction, temple, in, Jerusalem, -, BC, when, they, were, exiled, to, Babylonia, up, present, time
Category: noun.event
